



## Shortcodes

### Container and columns
Use container and column shortcodes inside template files like below.
Note the content has to be inline with the tags or 11ty may render it a code block.  It's just a weird rendering bug.

```html {% raw %}
  {% container %}
    {% column %}
    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit,
    {% endcolumn %}

    {% column %}
    Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur.
    {% endcolumn %}
  {% endcontainer %}
{% endraw %}
```

