### Images
Responsive images are generated responsively using either front matter data or as a shrotcode.

Copy an image to `/src/assets/images/` and follow the code below.

***Caveat: this shortcode does not render when used inside a partial that is included on a page. I know it's annoying...I'm trying to find a workaround.***

#### Shortcode
```html {% raw %}
{% image '/assets/images/Pusheen_Zoom_Backgrounds_room_2020.jpg', 'Its Pusheen', 'feature' %}
{% endraw %}
```


#### Front matter
```yaml
thumbnail:
  url: /assets/images/Pusheen_Zoom_Background_Campfire_2020.jpg
  alt: a pic
  classes: feature test asodhioas
```

