### Modals
An easily customisable modal is included in this boilerplate and can be used as a paired shortcode as below.
Note the indentation of the content with the template tags (again, a rendering issue)
{% raw %}
<pre>
{% modal content, modalName, buttonText %}
...content
{% endmodal %}
</pre>
{% endraw %}

```html {% raw %}
{# start modal markup #}
{% modal 'popup', 'Open Modal' %}
{% container %}
  {% column %}
  this is content generated inside a modal shortcode!
  {% endcolumn %}
  {% column %}
  this is content generated inside a modal shortcode!
  {% endcolumn %}
{% endcontainer%}
{% endmodal %}
{# end modal markup #}
{% endraw %}
```



